        "text_8eK3c3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Since 2018, Maximum Effort Academy has been at the forefront of speed and strength development. While our <strong>WhatsApp and Discord</strong> communities remain our go-to for instant alerts and daily session updates, social media is often too \"instant\"—valuable insights can be easily buried or forgotten in the feed.</p><p>In 2026, we made the strategic decision to centralise our core knowledge here. This hub is designed to complement our socials by providing a permanent home for:</p><ul><li><strong>In-Depth Research:</strong> Scientific coaching principles that require more than just a caption.</li><li><strong>Season Archives:</strong> Results that stay accessible long after the notification has disappeared.</li><li><strong>Technical Analysis:</strong> Drills and methodologies you can refer back to throughout your journey.</li><li>By moving our deep-dive content from social platforms to our own website, we ensure every athlete has 24/7 access to the foundational tools and history that define our Academy.</li></ul>"
          }
